        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. SEM study of Callicarpa gracilis Fewkes, 1881, unbranched morphotype (continued). A. Detail of an empty phylactocarp. B. Portion of a phylactocarp bearing gonothecae. C. Gonothecae, greatly enlarged. D. Three insertions of gonothecae on the proximal, adaxial side of a ramulus. E. Detail of adjacent ramuli. F. Distal end of a phylactocarp seen apically. All from sample MNHN-IK-2015-617. Scale bars: D = 50 µm; E = 100 µm; B, C = 200 µm; A, F = 500 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4529230/files/figure.png" .
